name: Joker
0:
”Alexa, ask my joker to tell me something about John”
”Alexa, ask my joker to tell a joke about Jane”
”Alexa, ask my joker find out something about Joe”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my joker
des: Want to hear something funny about a person? The joker skill gives you the opportunity hear a few lighthearted "facts" about the person you want to know. Just say "Alexa, ask my joker to tell me about John" to get started.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
